Lagos State Junior Model College Badore bụ ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị nke dị n'obodo Badore, mpaghara gọọmentị mpaghara Eti-Osa nke Lagos Steeti.
Tupu afọ 2003, ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị nke obere na nke okenye na Lagos Steeti bụ otu nchịkwa nchịkwa
Gọọmentị site na Ministri Mmụta nke Lagos Steeti nyere iwu ka e kewaa ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị niile dị na steeti ahụ na nke nta (JSS1-3) na nke okenye (SS1-3)
Nke a bụ ihe dugara n'ịmepụta Lagos State Junior Model College Badore site na Lagos State Model College Badora (nke e guzobere na 19 Febụwarị 1988) na Jenụwarị 6, 2003
Mpụta nke ụlọ akwụkwọ ọhụrụ ahụ mere ka a họpụta Mrs
Sidikat Titilayo Smith dị ka onye isi ụlọ akwụkwọ mbụ.
Lagos State Junior Model College Badore nwere ụlọ oriri na ọṅụṅụ nke na-anabata ụmụ akwụkwọ ya niile, si otú a na-arụ ọrụ naanị usoro ịbanye.
